green building council have partnered to accelerate green building growth in developing counties the target is to scale up green buildings over a sevenyear period until  of the property market is saturated certification occurs when the edge standard is met which requires  less energy water and materials than conventional homes see alsoedit environment health and safety global environment facility grassroots business fund multilateral investment guarantee agency referencesedit  a b c d ottenhoff jenny  international finance corporation report center for global development retrieved    a b c international finance corporation ifc history world bank group retrieved    madura jeff  international financial management abridged th edition mason oh thomson southwestern isbn    international finance corporation ifcs vision values  purpose world bank group retrieved    international finance corporation  ifc development goals pdf report world bank group retrieved    billions in out of control ifc investments into thirdparties causing human rights abuses around the world  oxfam international wwwoxfamorg retrieved    can you fight poverty with a fivestar hotel foreign policy retrieved    jacks allen  world bank head sees ifc start in early  the washington post p    a b cpi inflation calculator us bureau of labor statistics retrieved    ifc picks up  pc stake in angel broking live mint  october    ifc supports greek banks with € million intelligentnewscom  december  retrieved  december    a b c d e f g h i j international finance corporation  ifc annual report  where innovation meets impact report world bank group retrieved    a b c d e f g h i j k international finance corporation  ifc annual report  i am opportunity report world bank group retrieved    a b c international finance corporation  ifc organizational structure pdf report world bank group retrieved    update world bank taps jinyong cai to head private sector lender reuters  retrieved    chinese national to head world b