w down and quality and safety standards to slip p® lubricants provide a safe and easy way to improve automotive assembly operations more information  all industries  resources specially formulated cleaners for the water  wastewater industry formulated products that meet your membrane cleaning needs compatible with uf ro ceramic and nf systems today’s complex cleaning tasks make it difficult to find a consistently effective filter membrane cleaner our proprietary formulated cleaners work effectively at restoring  flux at safe ph ranges more information  all industries  resources specially formulated lubricants for the pump  hvac industry p® lubricants are the perfect solution for pump and seal repairs they have been used for years by treatment plant operators to maintain equipment and replace parts such as seals orings hoses grommets and plugs more information  all industries  resources specially formulated cleaners for the laboratory industry whether you need to remove biological debris fingerprints protein starch or dye our cleaners provide consistent results our laboratory cleaners are excellent for use on flasks pipettes slides stainless steel plastic and other laboratory equipment and surfaces when rinsed properly our cleaners leave absolutely no residue more information  all industries  resources specially formulated lubricants for the construction p® lubricants are used in the manufacturing and repair and maintenance of heavyduty construction vehicles rubber assembly applications include bushings leaf springs chassis and suspension components p® lubricants provide temporary lubrication to rubber or soft plastic parts more information  all industries  resources specially formulated cleaners for the pharmaceuticals  biotech our precision cleaners provide consistent results with every use and leave surfaces completely clean they have been proven effective in critical cleaning applications including mixing tanks tablet presses fluid lines batch process tanks filte