standards and build a better future for millions of people by offering investment advisory and asset management services to encourage private sector development in more than  developing countries looking toward its own future ifc recently renovated the interior of its squarefoot headquarters in washington dc nearly  staff members work in the triangularshaped building that is located just blocks from the white house among the areas upgraded was the squarefoot cafeteria which encompasses a kitchen as well as a serving and dining area modernizing the space included installing ilight plexineon white x k fixtures as a design element the led fixtures accent the vertical lines of structural columns that are located in the middle of what is now a more welcoming and contemporary common area   the design challenge rather than ignore the columns rtkl the project architect chose to embrace them careful traffic flow planning assures the columns are not a physical hindrance but a solution was still needed to make them less visually obtrusive working closely with rtkl architectural lighting design firm mcla suggested outlining the columns with plexineon which the firm had used successfully on prior projects “we talked about providing an illuminated reveal but we decided a luminous line of light would be more interesting” – frank feist senior designer at mcla   the plexineon advantage plexineon not only provided the even line of bright light that the team was envisioning it also helped that ilight was able to bend the fixtures to follow the four compound curves on each column “the plexineon really does accentuate the hourglass shape” feist says the result is transformative — plexineon adds lightness to the heavy columns accenting their sculptural nature once installed the design team was delighted that the fixtures provide a glow that’s more contemporary than nostalgic feist says “rather than look like neon the plexineon has a modern feel that’s perfect for what we were trying to achieve” the glow of plexineon white adds lightness to the heavy columns accenting their sculptural nature ifc cafeteria – high resolution download ifc cafeteria – low resolution download   project details project ifc headquarters site washington dc location interior application product use direct view lighting design mcla wwwmclainccom  architects rtkl wwwrtklcom product plexineon white x  length  lf  m case study pdf download to download this case study as a pdf please click here accentcorporatefinanceinteriorinternational finance corporation tweet ilight technologiesabout us architectural lighting download center technical specs product warranty case studies contact us plexineon color series plexineon white x series plexineon white x series hypnotica series “rgb” custom bending  signage inwall mounting accessories copyright   ilight technologies home about us products case studies terms and conditions contact us x subject message hey buddy i found this information for you international finance corporation here is the website link httpswwwilighttechcomifc thank you send ilight home products  day quick ship plexineon white series plexineon color series plexineon recessed mount system hypnotica series handrail lighting system dmx playback devices accessories plexineon bending signage  corners spellbrite led signage system ilight technologies gallery ilight installation gallery thumbnails case studies technical info technical specs plexineon hypnotica corners  cuttables bending capabilities signage power supplies wires  cables dmx playback devices dimming dmx playback devices network connectivity mounting hardware recessed mount system installation tools installation  wiring guides plexineon installation hypnotica installation photometricsies files turtle friendly weatherability  energy product warranty faq support product warranty find an architectural rep faq terms and conditions contact us about ilight technologies about us find an architectural rep international sales national accounts  sign companies news warranties  patents case study newsletter submit your photo contact us overview about ifc ifc governance leadership where we work east asia  the pacific europe  central asia latin america  the caribbean middle east  north africa south asia subsaharan africa western europe partnerships ifc history solutions expertise agribusiness  forestry financial institutions funds health  education infrastructure manufacturing oil gas  mining publicprivate partnerships telecoms media  technology tourism retail  property products  services loans equity trade  supplychain finance syndications treasury client solutions blended finance venture capital advisory asset management development impact sustainability env social  governance the business case resources for companies es policies and standards corporate governance esg accountability gender climate business projects news all news creating markets stories of impact postcards pressroom media contacts resources contacts english عربي 简体 français  português русский español about ifc overview we work with the private sector in developing countries to create markets that open up opportunities for all ifc a member of the world bank group is the largest global development institution focused exclusively on the private sector in developing countries we utilize and leverage our products and services—as well as products and services of other institutions in the world bank group—to provide development solutions customized to meet clients’ needs we apply our financial resources technical expertise global experience and innovative thinking to help our partners overcome financial operational and political challenges clients view ifc as a provider and mobilizer of scarce capital knowledge and longterm partnerships that can help address critical constraints in areas such as finance infrastructure employee skills and the regulatory environment ifc is also a leading mobilizer of thirdparty resources for its projects our willingness to engage in difficult environments and our leadership in crowdingin private finance enable us to extend our footprint and have a development impact well beyond our direct resources   our governance  our funding  investor relations  ifc history   what we bring innovation for more than half a century ifc has innovated to strengthen private sector development wherever it’s needed most influence as the world’s largest global development institution focused on the private sector ifc plays a significant role in influencing the course of private sector development demonstration we have a long history of setting a good example—of demonstrating the rewards of investing in challenging markets impact we go wherever we are needed most and deploy our resources wherever they will achieve the greatest impact   ifcs projects and programs are evaluated by the independent evaluation group accountability is ensured by the independent office of the compliance advisor ombudsman share ifc governancearticles of agreementfundinginvestor relationsleadershipwhere we workpartnershipsdevelopment partners  foundationsifc history aaeeccaefdbfbcfcediv   ifc user agreement general inquiry world bank group quick links for clients for investors for media for stakeholders for job seekers accountability disclosed projects compliance advisor ombudsman independent evaluation group ibrd ida ifc miga icsid